1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:29,980
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 10 =

20
00:01:33,260 --> 00:01:35,140
Yongshu. Yongshu.

21
00:01:35,660 --> 00:01:36,300
Zimei.

22
00:01:37,340 --> 00:01:37,940
Don’t dismount.

23
00:01:38,580 --> 00:01:40,020
Go straight to my place.

24
00:01:42,300 --> 00:01:44,020
You came top in the exam

25
00:01:44,020 --> 00:01:45,140
and have a beautiful wife.

26
00:01:45,140 --> 00:01:46,540
Tonight, you’re...

27
00:01:52,420 --> 00:01:53,940
Youheng and I are finally married.

28
00:01:54,820 --> 00:01:56,020
= Ouyang Xiu, courtesy name Yongshu =
I am excited.

29
00:01:56,700 --> 00:01:57,380
Yongshu,

30
00:01:57,940 --> 00:01:58,740
= Su Shunqin, courtesy name Zimei =
Youheng is at home

31
00:01:58,740 --> 00:01:59,820
preparing dinner as we speak,

32
00:01:59,820 --> 00:02:00,500
right?

33
00:02:01,220 --> 00:02:02,220
I’ve also invited

34
00:02:02,220 --> 00:02:03,380
other friends.

35
00:02:03,580 --> 00:02:05,100
Let’s drink till all’s blue tonight.

36
00:02:05,260 --> 00:02:06,060
No problem.

37
00:02:06,140 --> 00:02:06,780
Let’s go.

38
00:02:07,044 --> 00:02:07,938
- Hya! - Hya!

39
00:02:12,020 --> 00:02:13,310
One of the scholars who passed the exam

40
00:02:13,450 --> 00:02:15,610
is Su Yijian’s grandson Su Shunqin.

41
00:02:15,850 --> 00:02:17,090
He did surprise me.

42
00:02:17,770 --> 00:02:19,580
Since he was young, he and Mu Xiu

43
00:02:19,850 --> 00:02:21,310
have been opposed to flamboyance and obscurity.

44
00:02:21,450 --> 00:02:22,850
Ouyang Xiu followed in his steps.

45
00:02:23,300 --> 00:02:24,310
= Fu Bi, courtesy name Yanguo
Han Qi, courtesy name Zhigui =

46
00:02:24,320 --> 00:02:25,660
He isn’t afraid of others’ mockery.

47
00:02:25,660 --> 00:02:26,560
His works don’t follow a fixed form.

48
00:02:26,700 --> 00:02:28,800
His words are simple yet sharp.

49
00:02:29,370 --> 00:02:31,420
I’ve read quite a lot of his articles.

50
00:02:34,150 --> 00:02:36,480
Ouyang Xiu will soon work in the Capital.

51
00:02:36,900 --> 00:02:38,590
Su Shunqin passed the exam

52
00:02:38,700 --> 00:02:39,680
and can serve the court.

53
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:41,150
I’m sure

54
00:02:41,570 --> 00:02:42,750
they’ll lead

55
00:02:42,900 --> 00:02:44,350
the new literary trend.

56
00:02:47,620 --> 00:02:49,530
Fan Zhongyan disagreed with deposing
the former empress.

57
00:02:50,020 --> 00:02:51,460
Yet Lv Yijian insisted on driving him

58
00:02:51,500 --> 00:02:52,500
out of the Capital.

59
00:02:52,650 --> 00:02:54,720
Many officials found that unfair

60
00:02:56,570 --> 00:02:57,730
yet Fan Zhongyan

61
00:02:58,770 --> 00:03:00,410
didn’t seem to be angry.

62
00:03:01,570 --> 00:03:02,590
He even came up with

63
00:03:03,350 --> 00:03:05,340
that masterpiece

64
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:07,330
Ten Enjoyments in Tonglu.

65
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:10,530
That poem is indeed well-written

66
00:03:11,270 --> 00:03:12,620
but I prefer the other one called

67
00:03:12,620 --> 00:03:15,710
Following Ge Hong’s Flower Grafting Song.

68
00:03:42,860 --> 00:03:43,700
Your Highness

69
00:03:43,700 --> 00:03:45,060
Madam Miao, Madam Yang, Madam Yu

70
00:03:45,060 --> 00:03:45,940
came to pay respects.

71
00:03:48,620 --> 00:03:49,620
Send them in.

72
00:03:49,780 --> 00:03:50,420
Yes.

73
00:04:04,180 --> 00:04:05,660
My respects, Your Highness.

74
00:04:08,900 --> 00:04:10,140
Your Highness is the Empress.

75
00:04:10,300 --> 00:04:11,300
We don’t have

76
00:04:11,300 --> 00:04:12,700
valuable presents

77
00:04:12,860 --> 00:04:13,980
but could only bring you

78
00:04:13,980 --> 00:04:15,980
sachets, accessories

79
00:04:15,980 --> 00:04:16,940
and snacks we made

80
00:04:17,460 --> 00:04:18,700
to congratulate you.

81
00:04:19,260 --> 00:04:20,140
I also prepared

82
00:04:20,140 --> 00:04:21,220
gifts for you.

83
00:04:21,420 --> 00:04:22,740
I got them when I went hunting

84
00:04:22,740 --> 00:04:23,660
with my brothers before.

85
00:04:24,180 --> 00:04:24,980
Hunting?

86
00:04:26,340 --> 00:04:27,500
Your Highness could hunt?

87
00:04:28,620 --> 00:04:30,100
Your Highness came from a decorated family.

88
00:04:30,100 --> 00:04:31,140
The Caos

89
00:04:31,220 --> 00:04:32,820
are all-round talents.

90
00:04:33,380 --> 00:04:34,180
Have a seat.

91
00:04:37,100 --> 00:04:38,580
Which book are you copying?

92
00:04:39,140 --> 00:04:40,780
It’s not Commandments for Women
or Virtues for Women.

93
00:04:40,860 --> 00:04:41,980
nor is it a Buddhist text.

94
00:04:42,260 --> 00:04:44,140
It’s new to me.

95
00:04:47,740 --> 00:04:49,340
They’re recipes to cook pies.

96
00:04:51,380 --> 00:04:54,540
Plain pies, baked pies, stuffed pies...

97
00:04:54,980 --> 00:04:56,700
You’re reading a cook book.

98
00:04:58,620 --> 00:04:59,660
Taste the liquor.

99
00:05:08,940 --> 00:05:09,700
So good.

100
00:05:11,220 --> 00:05:12,820
My mother and I

101
00:05:12,820 --> 00:05:14,780
made this liquor according to the recipe.

102
00:05:15,140 --> 00:05:16,580
Then we changed the recipe

103
00:05:16,740 --> 00:05:17,740
to enrich its flavor.

104
00:05:18,660 --> 00:05:20,940
We also learned how to dry the meat

105
00:05:20,940 --> 00:05:21,940
to make dried meat slices

106
00:05:22,740 --> 00:05:23,940
and how to dry vegetables.

107
00:05:25,020 --> 00:05:25,860
Good!

108
00:05:26,940 --> 00:05:29,060
“I won’t cry to the wall like you” is wonderful.

109
00:05:53,700 --> 00:05:54,380
Han Qi,

110
00:05:55,140 --> 00:05:57,460
you love all sorts of entertainment, right?

111
00:05:58,140 --> 00:06:00,140
Have you watched puppet shows?

112
00:06:01,860 --> 00:06:04,300
Yes, I have.

113
00:06:05,020 --> 00:06:05,860
Your Majesty...

114
00:06:06,420 --> 00:06:07,940
Prepare a puppet show

115
00:06:08,620 --> 00:06:11,140
based on Mr. Fan and the gardener’s story.

116
00:06:12,180 --> 00:06:13,020
I’d like to invite Lv Yijian

117
00:06:14,620 --> 00:06:16,580
to watch it with me.

118
00:06:17,500 --> 00:06:18,140
Cheers.

119
00:06:18,140 --> 00:06:19,420
Cheers, everyone. Let’s drink.

120
00:06:22,860 --> 00:06:24,108
We’ve drunk enough.

121
00:06:28,980 --> 00:06:29,980
Let’s see if Zimei’s poem

122
00:06:29,980 --> 00:06:31,580
for this girl

123
00:06:31,780 --> 00:06:33,660
is better than Liu Sanbian’s.

124
00:06:35,500 --> 00:06:36,820
= Wang Gongchen, courtesy name Junkuang =
He dares not write it,

125
00:06:36,940 --> 00:06:37,700
or his wife

126
00:06:37,700 --> 00:06:38,940
won’t let him in tonight.

127
00:06:38,980 --> 00:06:40,060
Am I right?

128
00:06:40,460 --> 00:06:41,740
That’s not true.

129
00:06:42,380 --> 00:06:43,740
Prepare the stationery.

130
00:06:43,740 --> 00:06:44,380
Ouyang.

131
00:06:45,540 --> 00:06:46,700
Long time no see.

132
00:06:47,100 --> 00:06:48,980
You’ve become even more famous.

133
00:06:50,300 --> 00:06:53,020
My father-in-law loves your works.

134
00:06:53,020 --> 00:06:55,980
Whenever your new articles

135
00:06:56,100 --> 00:06:57,180
or poems come out,

136
00:06:57,460 --> 00:07:00,900
he’ll have them copied and shared with our family.

137
00:07:03,460 --> 00:07:07,860
I’m grateful

138
00:07:08,540 --> 00:07:10,940
for Mr. Xue’s appreciation.

139
00:07:12,180 --> 00:07:14,420
Last year, after my wife passed away,

140
00:07:14,980 --> 00:07:16,780
he also expressed his condolences.

141
00:07:18,300 --> 00:07:20,420
Before I came back to the Capital,

142
00:07:21,740 --> 00:07:22,980
he even sent the matchmaker

143
00:07:23,380 --> 00:07:25,620
to marry his fourth daughter to me.

144
00:07:28,620 --> 00:07:31,380
What do you say, Ouyang?

145
00:07:33,300 --> 00:07:34,380
Let’s drink first.

146
00:07:35,900 --> 00:07:36,540
Drink up.

147
00:07:36,660 --> 00:07:37,580
Don’t change the subject.

148
00:07:42,100 --> 00:07:45,620
Mr. Xue favors you more,

149
00:07:46,700 --> 00:07:47,460
doesn’t he?

150
00:07:48,300 --> 00:07:49,460
After his third daughter died,

151
00:07:50,500 --> 00:07:52,460
you married the fifth one

152
00:07:53,100 --> 00:07:54,700
and are still his son-in-law.

153
00:07:55,540 --> 00:07:58,740
The old son-in-law is also the new one.

154
00:08:04,100 --> 00:08:07,020
If I marry his fourth daughter,

155
00:08:09,140 --> 00:08:11,140
how should I call you?

156
00:08:12,380 --> 00:08:13,380
Won’t that make your rank

157
00:08:13,380 --> 00:08:16,580
lower than mine?

158
00:08:21,820 --> 00:08:23,020
Don’t take it to heart. Let’s go.

159
00:08:23,020 --> 00:08:23,700
Let’s drink.

160
00:08:24,220 --> 00:08:24,860
Su Zimei,

161
00:08:25,300 --> 00:08:25,980
are you done or not?

162
00:08:26,060 --> 00:08:27,140
I’m on it.

163
00:08:27,580 --> 00:08:28,460
Let me see.

164
00:08:31,860 --> 00:08:32,700
Finished.

165
00:08:35,220 --> 00:08:35,860
Good!

166
00:08:36,100 --> 00:08:37,820
Let’s drink.

167
00:08:42,900 --> 00:08:43,860
Yongshu is drunk.

168
00:08:45,740 --> 00:08:46,540
Stop drinking.

169
00:08:51,380 --> 00:08:52,060
Come on.

170
00:08:58,460 --> 00:09:00,620
Let’s go back, my lady.

171
00:09:00,860 --> 00:09:01,660
We shouldn’t be here.

172
00:09:02,660 --> 00:09:03,500
Why?

173
00:09:03,580 --> 00:09:04,340
What happened?

174
00:09:05,980 --> 00:09:07,420
They mocked your husband,

175
00:09:08,260 --> 00:09:10,780
saying he’s become the new son-in-law,

176
00:09:11,100 --> 00:09:13,980
= Wang Gongchen’s wife, Xue Yuhu =
and something about ranks.

177
00:09:21,180 --> 00:09:22,380
Good. Not bad at all.

178
00:09:23,300 --> 00:09:24,220
It’s beautiful.

179
00:09:29,740 --> 00:09:30,380
Let’s go.

180
00:09:31,020 --> 00:09:31,900
Let’s go home.

181
00:09:44,820 --> 00:09:46,260
♪ What makes you say that ♪

182
00:09:46,500 --> 00:09:48,820
♪ Life is full of ups and downs ♪

183
00:09:49,300 --> 00:09:50,140
♪ Just like you ♪

184
00:09:50,620 --> 00:09:51,940
♪ Who have highs ♪

185
00:09:52,420 --> 00:09:53,980
♪ And lows ♪

186
00:09:54,540 --> 00:09:57,060
♪ Although you were exiled ♪

187
00:09:57,380 --> 00:10:01,980
♪ You could also be summoned back ♪

188
00:10:02,740 --> 00:10:04,540
♪ Be summoned back ♪

189
00:10:05,940 --> 00:10:07,900
♪ It’s possible ♪

190
00:10:07,900 --> 00:10:08,900
Hearing that accent,

191
00:10:10,500 --> 00:10:13,020
I feel as if Fan Zhongyan were back.

192
00:10:13,700 --> 00:10:18,780
♪ We’re both miserable ♪

193
00:10:23,900 --> 00:10:26,380
♪ That upsets me ♪

194
00:10:26,940 --> 00:10:30,020
♪ I had a spot at court ♪

195
00:10:30,940 --> 00:10:33,740
♪ Yet I was asked to leave ♪

196
00:10:34,220 --> 00:10:38,860
♪ I won’t cry to the wall like you ♪

197
00:10:40,700 --> 00:10:41,540
Good!

198
00:10:42,860 --> 00:10:44,820
That’s admirable.

199
00:10:44,820 --> 00:10:47,420
♪ Gains and losses will disappear eventually ♪

200
00:10:48,100 --> 00:10:51,460
♪ Who can control heaven and earth♪

201
00:10:52,900 --> 00:10:55,100
I was moved by Fan Zhongyan’s spirit

202
00:10:55,580 --> 00:10:56,460
and lost control of myself.

203
00:10:57,020 --> 00:10:57,860
Don’t worry.

204
00:10:58,540 --> 00:10:59,820
We aren’t at court.

205
00:11:01,900 --> 00:11:03,980
This poem by Fan Zhongyan

206
00:11:04,220 --> 00:11:05,340
and Pipa Song

207
00:11:05,340 --> 00:11:06,620
by Bai Juyi

208
00:11:06,940 --> 00:11:08,100
are similar in many ways.

209
00:11:09,380 --> 00:11:10,980
Their stories are similar.

210
00:11:11,980 --> 00:11:14,380
While Bai Juyi cried

211
00:11:14,740 --> 00:11:16,940
after hearing the singer’s story,

212
00:11:17,740 --> 00:11:19,420
Fan Zhongyan says “I won’t cry”

213
00:11:19,420 --> 00:11:22,060
after learning the gardener’s misfortune.

214
00:11:22,940 --> 00:11:24,620
Quality aside,

215
00:11:24,980 --> 00:11:27,340
Fang Zhongyan’s spirit

216
00:11:27,660 --> 00:11:29,900
should be learned by us.

217
00:11:36,700 --> 00:11:37,580
In my opinion,

218
00:11:38,100 --> 00:11:39,060
it’s not just

219
00:11:39,060 --> 00:11:40,580
that Fan Zhongyan has a broader mind

220
00:11:40,580 --> 00:11:41,860
and is more ambitious,

221
00:11:42,020 --> 00:11:43,860
but when demoted,

222
00:11:43,940 --> 00:11:45,300
Bai Juyi didn’t serve

223
00:11:45,340 --> 00:11:47,220
under a great emperor.

224
00:11:48,020 --> 00:11:49,740
Emperor Xianzong of Tang was ambitious

225
00:11:49,740 --> 00:11:51,260
but he refused to take advice.

226
00:11:51,380 --> 00:11:52,820
Bai Juyi cared about the masses

227
00:11:52,820 --> 00:11:53,820
= Wen Yanbo, courtesy name Kuanfu =
and was eager to help them

228
00:11:53,820 --> 00:11:54,860
but only got framed.

229
00:11:54,860 --> 00:11:56,900
He became dispirited after exiled to Jiangzhou.

230
00:11:57,900 --> 00:11:59,540
Fan Zhongyan’s demotion is only temporary.

231
00:11:59,620 --> 00:12:01,780
He knows Your Majesty is benevolent

232
00:12:01,820 --> 00:12:02,860
and is willing to take others’ advice,

233
00:12:03,300 --> 00:12:04,660
so he has faith in Your Majesty

234
00:12:04,660 --> 00:12:06,700
and the court.

235
00:12:09,900 --> 00:12:11,980
By complimenting me,

236
00:12:12,300 --> 00:12:13,700
he’s forcing me to be humble.

237
00:12:14,820 --> 00:12:17,660
Those are all my heartfelt words.

238
00:12:20,780 --> 00:12:25,860
♪ I hope I can leave ♪

239
00:12:29,260 --> 00:12:34,180
♪ Once you’re freed ♪

240
00:12:34,180 --> 00:12:37,340
Fan was demoted for supporting the former empress.

241
00:12:38,420 --> 00:12:39,660
That incident is over.

242
00:12:40,660 --> 00:12:41,380
Now,

243
00:12:41,540 --> 00:12:43,740
Empress Cao you chose

244
00:12:45,620 --> 00:12:48,100
is elegant and well-mannered.

245
00:12:48,700 --> 00:12:49,420
I think

246
00:12:50,020 --> 00:12:52,060
supporters of the former empress,

247
00:12:52,060 --> 00:12:54,220
such as Fan Zhongyan and Yu Jing, will admit

248
00:12:54,500 --> 00:12:58,140
that Empress Cao is a better role model.

249
00:12:59,700 --> 00:13:01,020
You’re right, Your Majesty.

250
00:13:01,940 --> 00:13:05,180
Fan Zhongyan must’ve realized his fault.

251
00:13:07,540 --> 00:13:09,980
Fan Zhongyan is honest and capable.

252
00:13:10,740 --> 00:13:11,820
He only made that mistake

253
00:13:11,820 --> 00:13:12,980
because he was worried about the state.

254
00:13:14,220 --> 00:13:17,140
While he’s outside the Capital, he’s built schools

255
00:13:17,260 --> 00:13:18,300
and regulated rivers.

256
00:13:18,820 --> 00:13:21,620
He’s diligent and made remarkable achievements.

257
00:13:22,500 --> 00:13:23,540
If he has no other mistakes,

258
00:13:23,580 --> 00:13:25,420
we should summon him back

259
00:13:25,500 --> 00:13:26,820
to work in the ministries.

260
00:13:33,060 --> 00:13:34,940
I agree, Your Majesty.

261
00:13:35,300 --> 00:13:37,020
Lesson learned.

262
00:13:37,860 --> 00:13:41,180
I’ll discuss it with other colleagues.

263
00:13:41,740 --> 00:13:43,260
If there’s a vacancy for him,

264
00:13:44,540 --> 00:13:46,740
he can come back to the Capital.

265
00:13:55,860 --> 00:13:59,300
= Hall of Peace =

266
00:14:11,820 --> 00:14:13,380
I brought this from home.

267
00:14:13,780 --> 00:14:15,260
There’s a bigger one there.

268
00:14:16,780 --> 00:14:18,020
There are some silkworms.

269
00:14:18,020 --> 00:14:19,340
You can raise them yourselves.

270
00:14:21,220 --> 00:14:23,180
We have mulberries in the palace.

271
00:14:23,340 --> 00:14:24,820
Empress Dowager used to tell consorts...

272
00:14:24,820 --> 00:14:25,620
His Majesty has arrived.

273
00:14:30,820 --> 00:14:31,460
Your Majesty.

274
00:14:31,460 --> 00:14:32,340
- Your Majesty. - Your Majesty.

275
00:14:34,820 --> 00:14:36,620
We’ve been here for too long

276
00:14:36,620 --> 00:14:38,380
drinking liquor and reading books.

277
00:14:39,780 --> 00:14:40,620
We should take our leave.

278
00:14:59,300 --> 00:15:00,260
You made the liquor?

279
00:15:02,500 --> 00:15:05,180
May I have a cup?

280
00:15:08,020 --> 00:15:09,180
It’s my pleasure.

281
00:17:43,100 --> 00:17:44,060
Books like Essential Arts for People’s Welfare

282
00:17:44,060 --> 00:17:45,460
and Yellow Emperor’s Inner Cannon

283
00:17:45,460 --> 00:17:46,620
are more useful to people

284
00:17:46,780 --> 00:17:47,820
than The Analects of Confucius

285
00:17:47,900 --> 00:17:48,580
and The Book of Songs.

286
00:17:48,700 --> 00:17:50,580
More copies should be made.

287
00:17:51,140 --> 00:17:53,020
I ordered the three ministries to allocate funds

288
00:17:53,020 --> 00:17:54,340
to print medical books last year.

289
00:17:54,380 --> 00:17:55,380
I know.

290
00:17:57,140 --> 00:17:59,020
How did you know that?

291
00:18:01,940 --> 00:18:02,980
I happened to learn that

292
00:18:02,980 --> 00:18:04,260
from my brother.

293
00:18:07,260 --> 00:18:08,260
Other than medical books,

294
00:18:08,260 --> 00:18:10,420
we need architecture and weaponry books.

295
00:18:11,220 --> 00:18:13,300
For example, before constructing a building,

296
00:18:13,300 --> 00:18:14,180
there should be a budget

297
00:18:14,380 --> 00:18:17,700
about materials needed

298
00:18:18,180 --> 00:18:19,500
so that the process won’t be delayed

299
00:18:19,500 --> 00:18:20,540
due to lack of materials

300
00:18:20,540 --> 00:18:22,580
and it’ll reduce waste.

301
00:18:24,140 --> 00:18:26,300
Danshu, I’m surprised

302
00:18:26,820 --> 00:18:28,140
that you know machines

303
00:18:28,260 --> 00:18:29,420
and farming, too.

304
00:18:29,780 --> 00:18:31,540
You must’ve been to many places

305
00:18:31,540 --> 00:18:32,740
with your father and brothers.

306
00:18:56,860 --> 00:18:59,020
Is it your time to rest?

307
00:19:09,820 --> 00:19:11,060
You must be tired, too.

308
00:19:11,820 --> 00:19:12,980
It’s windy.

309
00:19:13,620 --> 00:19:14,900
I’ll ask Huan

310
00:19:15,020 --> 00:19:16,500
to bring you a wind-proof lamp.

311
00:19:29,980 --> 00:19:30,620
Yes.

312
00:19:31,500 --> 00:19:34,820
I still have some reports to review.

313
00:20:05,620 --> 00:20:06,300
Your Majesty.

314
00:20:06,780 --> 00:20:07,620
What brings you here?

315
00:20:08,980 --> 00:20:10,500
Liaozi send me a message

316
00:20:10,860 --> 00:20:11,660
that you had dismissed

317
00:20:11,660 --> 00:20:12,540
everyone around you,

318
00:20:12,860 --> 00:20:14,020
including him.

319
00:20:14,740 --> 00:20:15,420
He was worried

320
00:20:15,820 --> 00:20:17,300
if he was reckless.

321
00:20:22,380 --> 00:20:23,300
Maoze,

322
00:20:23,940 --> 00:20:25,060
is Danshu

323
00:20:25,620 --> 00:20:27,100
still mad at me

324
00:20:27,300 --> 00:20:28,500
about the wedding night...

325
00:20:36,220 --> 00:20:39,060
Empress should be tolerant.

326
00:20:39,380 --> 00:20:40,780
No matter what you do,

327
00:20:40,900 --> 00:20:42,060
she shouldn’t hold a grudge.

328
00:20:44,420 --> 00:20:46,900
But I think

329
00:20:48,060 --> 00:20:51,500
she must be upset.

330
00:21:04,700 --> 00:21:05,900
Just now, we were chatting

331
00:21:06,060 --> 00:21:07,740
till about bedtime,

332
00:21:07,980 --> 00:21:08,780
yet she didn’t

333
00:21:11,340 --> 00:21:12,820
ask me to stay.

334
00:21:13,980 --> 00:21:15,380
If you insist,

335
00:21:16,300 --> 00:21:17,660
how could she reject you?

336
00:21:23,020 --> 00:21:24,220
I don’t want to force her.

337
00:21:29,620 --> 00:21:30,980
I won’t force her.

338
00:22:02,820 --> 00:22:03,500
Your Highness,

339
00:22:04,900 --> 00:22:08,140
His Majesty didn’t want to leave.

340
00:22:08,580 --> 00:22:09,860
You love him.

341
00:22:10,500 --> 00:22:11,820
Why didn’t you let him stay?

342
00:22:16,380 --> 00:22:17,460
I do love him.

343
00:22:20,980 --> 00:22:22,420
Before we married,

344
00:22:24,380 --> 00:22:25,820
he had my full attention.

345
00:22:28,380 --> 00:22:29,460
When I couldn’t see him,

346
00:22:30,900 --> 00:22:32,460
I’d keep track of his orders,

347
00:22:35,100 --> 00:22:36,900
such as printing medical books.

348
00:22:43,580 --> 00:22:45,100
But he has no feelings for me.

349
00:22:50,100 --> 00:22:52,220
I traveled a lot with my family.

350
00:22:54,980 --> 00:22:56,340
I didn’t know until today

351
00:22:58,260 --> 00:22:59,660
that before I came,

352
00:23:02,500 --> 00:23:04,860
he was in love with

353
00:23:06,500 --> 00:23:07,660
a merchant’s daughter.

354
00:23:10,020 --> 00:23:11,380
She also visited many places.

355
00:23:17,100 --> 00:23:19,460
That’s all in the past.

356
00:23:20,180 --> 00:23:21,540
His Majesty has sent her away.

357
00:23:21,540 --> 00:23:22,820
Only because they weren’t allowed to marry.

358
00:23:31,060 --> 00:23:32,660
He married me against his will.

359
00:23:42,260 --> 00:23:44,460
He left me alone on our wedding night.

360
00:23:49,980 --> 00:23:51,900
I must’ve reminded him of her

361
00:23:53,380 --> 00:23:55,340
because I understand machines, too,

362
00:23:55,340 --> 00:23:56,940
so he wants to stay as if she were still here.

363
00:24:02,380 --> 00:24:03,340
Is my place

364
00:24:03,340 --> 00:24:04,740
where he can come and go

365
00:24:05,540 --> 00:24:06,980
as he pleases?

366
00:24:16,580 --> 00:24:17,340
Your Highness,

367
00:24:18,500 --> 00:24:19,340
His Majesty...

368
00:24:21,420 --> 00:24:23,020
His Majesty is the Emperor after all.

369
00:24:23,500 --> 00:24:25,340
You can’t be too petty.

370
00:24:33,220 --> 00:24:34,060
Yes.

371
00:24:38,460 --> 00:24:40,220
You’re right. What’s wrong with me?

372
00:24:43,860 --> 00:24:46,180
That day, I already told myself

373
00:24:48,580 --> 00:24:50,380
to be a good empress.

374
00:24:54,380 --> 00:24:55,460
He’s the ruler of this state.

375
00:24:58,220 --> 00:25:00,260
Although I’m his wife,

376
00:25:00,260 --> 00:25:01,420
I also answer to him.

377
00:25:07,020 --> 00:25:07,820
No.

378
00:25:10,180 --> 00:25:12,260
Since he doesn’t want me to be his wife,

379
00:25:23,340 --> 00:25:25,500
I’ll do my best to help him.

380
00:25:29,220 --> 00:25:30,340
I used to wonder

381
00:25:30,340 --> 00:25:31,820
why I couldn’t be a man

382
00:25:31,820 --> 00:25:32,860
to assist him.

383
00:25:38,020 --> 00:25:38,740
Now,

384
00:25:41,220 --> 00:25:43,100
helping him manage the harem

385
00:25:44,980 --> 00:25:46,020
as his assistant

386
00:25:48,300 --> 00:25:49,660
is good enough.

387
00:25:54,980 --> 00:25:56,140
It’s good enough.

388
00:25:58,540 --> 00:25:59,260
Huan.

389
00:26:02,140 --> 00:26:03,180
Help me tidy myself.

390
00:26:04,620 --> 00:26:06,740
I can’t be seen red-eyed tomorrow.

391
00:26:07,900 --> 00:26:09,100
I must always be elegant.

392
00:26:11,420 --> 00:26:12,140
Yes.

393
00:26:35,580 --> 00:26:37,340
Guo banged her head on the pillar

394
00:26:37,540 --> 00:26:38,500
after hearing the promotion of a new empress.

395
00:26:38,940 --> 00:26:40,340
She survived but caught a cold afterwards

396
00:26:40,340 --> 00:26:41,220
yet she refused to take any medicine.

397
00:26:41,940 --> 00:26:43,940
Sir, she used to be the Empress after all.

398
00:26:44,780 --> 00:26:45,860
His Majesty also said

399
00:26:45,860 --> 00:26:47,220
to treat her well.

400
00:26:47,980 --> 00:26:49,660
We should report to His Majesty

401
00:26:50,180 --> 00:26:51,580
= Yan Wenying =
about her attempted suicide and illness.

402
00:26:51,860 --> 00:26:52,980
That happened inside the harem

403
00:26:53,060 --> 00:26:54,500
and should be reported to the Empress

404
00:26:54,500 --> 00:26:55,460
to let her decide.

405
00:26:56,100 --> 00:26:58,260
But...she was new in the palace.

406
00:26:58,660 --> 00:27:00,900
Guo is her predecessor.

407
00:27:01,180 --> 00:27:02,100
What if...

408
00:27:05,220 --> 00:27:07,460
Are you showing contempt for Ma’am

409
00:27:08,060 --> 00:27:09,860
simply because she was new

410
00:27:10,660 --> 00:27:12,580
or are you suspecting if she can

411
00:27:13,140 --> 00:27:14,500
handle it fairly.

412
00:27:15,980 --> 00:27:16,740
I dare not.

413
00:27:21,420 --> 00:27:24,220
Alright. I see.

414
00:27:25,980 --> 00:27:29,020
Your Highness, Consort Jing hurt herself

415
00:27:29,020 --> 00:27:30,380
only to win His Majesty’s attention.

416
00:27:30,780 --> 00:27:31,980
She knows he’s kindhearted.

417
00:27:32,260 --> 00:27:34,300
Back then, although she committed

418
00:27:34,300 --> 00:27:35,380
a felony,

419
00:27:35,740 --> 00:27:37,740
His Majesty was still sad when demoting her

420
00:27:38,060 --> 00:27:39,340
and he told Zhang Maoze

421
00:27:39,340 --> 00:27:40,580
to take good care of her

422
00:27:40,580 --> 00:27:41,420
and can’t mistreat her.

423
00:27:42,260 --> 00:27:44,220
This time, she made a huge scene

424
00:27:44,300 --> 00:27:46,220
only to have His Majesty pity her

425
00:27:46,340 --> 00:27:47,540
for old times’ sake.

426
00:27:51,500 --> 00:27:52,700
As far as I know,

427
00:27:53,820 --> 00:27:55,180
she was barren

428
00:27:55,740 --> 00:27:57,740
and decided to move to the nunnery herself,

429
00:27:58,740 --> 00:28:01,460
so she was demoted to Consort Jing.

430
00:28:02,180 --> 00:28:02,980
Who said

431
00:28:02,980 --> 00:28:04,580
she had committed a felony?

432
00:28:05,740 --> 00:28:06,660
Did His Majesty say so

433
00:28:08,020 --> 00:28:09,380
or the imperial decree?

434
00:28:25,340 --> 00:28:26,420
This is your first offense.

435
00:28:27,940 --> 00:28:31,180
You must’ve assumed

436
00:28:31,180 --> 00:28:33,660
I’m too young to know anything.

437
00:28:34,940 --> 00:28:37,060
Let me be clear.

438
00:28:38,060 --> 00:28:40,140
If you come to me to accuse anyone,

439
00:28:40,780 --> 00:28:41,900
show me the proof.

440
00:28:43,300 --> 00:28:45,580
Making groundless accusations,

441
00:28:46,300 --> 00:28:47,820
especially against those superior to you,

442
00:28:48,940 --> 00:28:51,820
will not be tolerated.

443
00:28:52,220 --> 00:28:54,260
I’m sorry. I won’t do it again.

444
00:28:55,940 --> 00:28:56,940
You may leave.

445
00:28:57,980 --> 00:28:58,820
I’ll discuss this matter

446
00:28:59,620 --> 00:29:00,980
with His Majesty

447
00:29:00,980 --> 00:29:01,900
and come up with a decision.

448
00:29:02,860 --> 00:29:03,620
Yes.

449
00:29:11,260 --> 00:29:15,700
= I won’t cry to the wall like you =

450
00:29:20,300 --> 00:29:22,451
= Liaozi =

451
00:29:22,460 --> 00:29:24,020
Your Majesty, Ma’am is outside.

452
00:29:29,260 --> 00:29:30,260
Let her in.

453
00:29:30,420 --> 00:29:31,140
Yes.

454
00:29:46,500 --> 00:29:47,220
Your Majesty.

455
00:29:49,500 --> 00:29:50,740
What brings you here today?

456
00:29:51,180 --> 00:29:52,620
You’ve been in the palace for almost a year

457
00:29:52,900 --> 00:29:54,140
but this is your first time coming here.

458
00:29:56,420 --> 00:29:57,380
Serve the wine

459
00:29:57,380 --> 00:29:58,340
from the west.

460
00:29:59,140 --> 00:29:59,820
Yes.

461
00:30:03,660 --> 00:30:04,820
I’m here

462
00:30:06,660 --> 00:30:07,780
for Consort Jing.

463
00:30:29,340 --> 00:30:30,340
Is there anything wrong with me?

464
00:30:32,060 --> 00:30:33,100
I’m curious

465
00:30:33,660 --> 00:30:35,860
why your name is Liaozi.

466
00:30:36,580 --> 00:30:38,740
I thought that name was for tea servants.

467
00:30:39,220 --> 00:30:40,260
You aren’t one of them.

468
00:30:41,980 --> 00:30:42,980
I used to be.

469
00:30:43,860 --> 00:30:44,820
There are so many of them

470
00:30:44,940 --> 00:30:46,420
in the palace.

471
00:30:46,900 --> 00:30:48,220
Are they all called Liaozi?

472
00:30:48,660 --> 00:30:49,740
How can others tell them apart?

473
00:30:51,220 --> 00:30:52,420
That’s only my name.

474
00:30:52,940 --> 00:30:53,700
Why?

475
00:30:56,660 --> 00:30:59,940
When I used to serve tea,

476
00:31:00,380 --> 00:31:01,220
one day,

477
00:31:02,220 --> 00:31:03,500
His Majesty and a few officials

478
00:31:03,980 --> 00:31:05,940
had a meeting in the Hall of Arch.

479
00:31:07,060 --> 00:31:08,300
He became thirsty in the middle

480
00:31:08,740 --> 00:31:11,180
and looked back at me for tea.

481
00:31:11,900 --> 00:31:13,180
When he saw I was sleepy,

482
00:31:13,660 --> 00:31:14,660
he chose to say nothing.

483
00:31:16,060 --> 00:31:18,420
He didn’t drink anything until Madam Miao

484
00:31:19,820 --> 00:31:22,060
gave him tea four hours later after the meeting.

485
00:31:23,580 --> 00:31:24,820
His Majesty told others

486
00:31:25,180 --> 00:31:26,940
about that as a joke.

487
00:31:27,980 --> 00:31:28,860
Then

488
00:31:29,580 --> 00:31:30,900
everyone in the Pavilion of Phoenix

489
00:31:31,060 --> 00:31:33,060
started to call me Liaozi.

490
00:31:33,860 --> 00:31:34,620
Later on,

491
00:31:35,260 --> 00:31:36,660
others all called me that.

492
00:31:37,660 --> 00:31:38,780
My original name

493
00:31:39,060 --> 00:31:40,100
was abandoned.

494
00:31:41,580 --> 00:31:42,660
Oh, I see.

495
00:31:44,060 --> 00:31:45,220
Why didn’t His Majesty wake you up?

496
00:31:46,780 --> 00:31:48,100
Had he done that,

497
00:31:48,740 --> 00:31:50,540
everyone would’ve known I was sleepy.

498
00:31:54,620 --> 00:31:56,420
He’d rather endure the thirst

499
00:31:56,740 --> 00:31:57,820
just so you wouldn’t be punished.

500
00:32:01,060 --> 00:32:01,900
Oh, my!

501
00:32:02,580 --> 00:32:03,700
He’s a good man.

502
00:32:04,220 --> 00:32:05,820
No wonder Ma’am adores him so much.

503
00:32:07,060 --> 00:32:08,300
I was new in the palace

504
00:32:08,700 --> 00:32:10,220
and know little about the past,

505
00:32:10,380 --> 00:32:11,380
so I dare not decide.

506
00:32:12,220 --> 00:32:13,380
After careful consideration,

507
00:32:13,900 --> 00:32:16,500
I think you should know about this

508
00:32:16,700 --> 00:32:17,980
and decide it yourself.

509
00:32:27,380 --> 00:32:28,140
I guess

510
00:32:28,580 --> 00:32:31,220
I owe you an apology.

511
00:32:54,700 --> 00:32:57,700
Two months ago,

512
00:32:59,780 --> 00:33:01,780
hearing that Guo was crying all day,

513
00:33:02,500 --> 00:33:03,700
I became softhearted

514
00:33:05,540 --> 00:33:07,020
and asked Maoze to visit her

515
00:33:09,900 --> 00:33:11,380
to bring her back in secret.

516
00:33:14,620 --> 00:33:18,140
Although she’s no longer the Empress,

517
00:33:19,020 --> 00:33:20,380
she’s still a consort.

518
00:33:21,740 --> 00:33:22,940
According to my knowledge,

519
00:33:23,460 --> 00:33:24,540
she moved to the nunnery

520
00:33:24,900 --> 00:33:26,460
to pacify her mind.

521
00:33:27,060 --> 00:33:28,180
It was her own decision.

522
00:33:28,980 --> 00:33:30,300
Now that she was unhappy there

523
00:33:30,700 --> 00:33:32,420
and you’re willing to have her back,

524
00:33:33,140 --> 00:33:34,700
it’s nothing wrong.

525
00:33:59,980 --> 00:34:01,420
Did I

526
00:34:04,180 --> 00:34:05,500
say something wrong?

527
00:34:09,980 --> 00:34:10,780
Danshu,

528
00:34:12,780 --> 00:34:13,780
you really think so?

529
00:34:16,780 --> 00:34:18,140
Both of us were summoned to the palace

530
00:34:20,260 --> 00:34:21,740
and appointed Empress.

531
00:34:25,300 --> 00:34:26,460
I pity her.

532
00:34:30,300 --> 00:34:31,140
What?

533
00:34:48,660 --> 00:34:51,020
Since you’re here for this matter

534
00:34:52,380 --> 00:34:53,620
and are honest with me,

535
00:34:57,140 --> 00:34:59,580
I’ll share our past

536
00:34:59,580 --> 00:35:00,780
with you

537
00:35:01,980 --> 00:35:03,460
and explain to you

538
00:35:04,460 --> 00:35:05,900
why I demoted her.

539
00:35:08,260 --> 00:35:08,980
After all,

540
00:35:12,780 --> 00:35:13,940
we’re a couple.

541
00:35:20,060 --> 00:35:21,580
His Majesty is always like this.

542
00:35:22,060 --> 00:35:23,020
He’s extremely kind

543
00:35:23,380 --> 00:35:24,700
and treats us well.

544
00:35:25,580 --> 00:35:26,940
I’ve never seen him punishing anyone

545
00:35:27,180 --> 00:35:29,300
due to negligence.

546
00:35:30,980 --> 00:35:32,180
Ma’am is the same.

547
00:35:32,500 --> 00:35:33,740
She treats us even better.

548
00:35:34,100 --> 00:35:35,460
She taught us knowledge.

549
00:35:36,260 --> 00:35:38,220
We even sneaked out to ride horses.

550
00:35:43,900 --> 00:35:44,740
That’s why

551
00:35:46,060 --> 00:35:47,100
Guo would never be

552
00:35:47,100 --> 00:35:48,260
a good empress.

553
00:35:48,540 --> 00:35:50,100
I don’t regret demoting her

554
00:35:51,300 --> 00:35:53,580
but she’s blunt

555
00:35:53,620 --> 00:35:54,780
and she’s never harmed anyone.

556
00:35:55,900 --> 00:35:58,380
Her only fault is entering the palace.

557
00:35:59,580 --> 00:36:00,420
That’s why

558
00:36:00,700 --> 00:36:03,660
I don’t want to see her suffer

559
00:36:04,260 --> 00:36:05,900
and grow old alone.

560
00:36:07,180 --> 00:36:08,540
I agree.

561
00:36:11,140 --> 00:36:12,300
I also think

562
00:36:13,460 --> 00:36:14,940
she should come back.

563
00:36:19,660 --> 00:36:21,340
I gave her the chance

564
00:36:22,180 --> 00:36:23,180
but she turned it down.

565
00:36:24,260 --> 00:36:25,020
She said

566
00:36:26,380 --> 00:36:28,220
everyone knows she’s been abandoned.

567
00:36:28,860 --> 00:36:30,220
She would agree to come back

568
00:36:30,580 --> 00:36:31,940
but not in secret.

569
00:36:33,900 --> 00:36:35,220
If she comes back

570
00:36:35,980 --> 00:36:37,020
without a proper title,

571
00:36:38,100 --> 00:36:39,740
how could she

572
00:36:40,100 --> 00:36:41,180
live with other consorts?

573
00:36:43,100 --> 00:36:44,220
You have a point.

574
00:36:45,060 --> 00:36:46,340
I was reckless.

575
00:36:48,060 --> 00:36:50,140
Well, we all have our own fate.

576
00:36:50,900 --> 00:36:52,020
I’ll tell Maoze

577
00:36:52,020 --> 00:36:53,580
to pay more attention to her

578
00:36:53,780 --> 00:36:55,060
and double

579
00:36:55,060 --> 00:36:56,020
all her supplies

580
00:36:56,340 --> 00:36:58,460
and assign more servants to her.

581
00:36:58,660 --> 00:37:00,180
She can come back

582
00:37:02,780 --> 00:37:06,020
by giving her a promotion.

583
00:37:08,180 --> 00:37:09,260
It’s doable.

584
00:37:15,500 --> 00:37:16,540
I understand

585
00:37:17,340 --> 00:37:19,860
that once she’s back,

586
00:37:20,180 --> 00:37:21,300
her rank will be lower than mine.

587
00:37:22,340 --> 00:37:24,020
She used to be in my position

588
00:37:25,140 --> 00:37:27,500
and she’s strong-willed.

589
00:37:27,740 --> 00:37:29,020
It’s hard for us to get along.

590
00:37:30,580 --> 00:37:32,500
But as the Empress,

591
00:37:32,900 --> 00:37:33,900
I’ll encounter

592
00:37:34,260 --> 00:37:35,820
endless difficulties in my life.

593
00:37:36,460 --> 00:37:37,620
One more won’t make any difference.

594
00:37:44,220 --> 00:37:45,860
Thank you, Danshu.

595
00:37:48,460 --> 00:37:50,980
This is what I should do.

596
00:37:54,060 --> 00:37:54,900
Your Majesty.

597
00:37:56,020 --> 00:37:58,540
If a promotion is granted to Guo,

598
00:37:59,460 --> 00:38:01,660
allow me to make another request.

599
00:38:03,740 --> 00:38:04,540
What is it?

600
00:38:06,300 --> 00:38:08,060
Madam Miao and the other two

601
00:38:08,580 --> 00:38:09,860
have been in the palace for years.

602
00:38:10,580 --> 00:38:12,420
They’ve been friendly and well-behaved.

603
00:38:12,700 --> 00:38:13,700
Also, they’ve never made mistakes

604
00:38:14,140 --> 00:38:15,500
when serving the Empress Dowager

605
00:38:16,060 --> 00:38:17,340
and senior consorts.

606
00:38:18,860 --> 00:38:19,980
I suggest

607
00:38:21,780 --> 00:38:23,700
they should be promoted, too.

608
00:38:27,100 --> 00:38:27,860
Good idea.

609
00:38:28,980 --> 00:38:30,540
Others aside,

610
00:38:30,900 --> 00:38:31,620
Xinhe

611
00:38:32,140 --> 00:38:33,740
is the closest to me since I was little.

612
00:38:34,300 --> 00:38:35,340
Years have passed,

613
00:38:35,620 --> 00:38:36,700
yet her rank has remained the same.

614
00:38:37,180 --> 00:38:38,020
She deserves more.

615
00:38:39,660 --> 00:38:41,060
You’re more thoughtful than me.

616
00:38:56,100 --> 00:38:57,380
That’s all

617
00:38:58,900 --> 00:39:00,300
that I’m here for.

618
00:39:02,260 --> 00:39:03,700
Your Majesty must still be busy.

619
00:39:04,180 --> 00:39:05,820
I’ll take my leave then.

620
00:39:06,860 --> 00:39:08,620
Thank you for your wine.

621
00:39:09,220 --> 00:39:11,580
Once my Moyao liquor is mature enough,

622
00:39:11,980 --> 00:39:13,180
we can taste it together.

623
00:40:04,820 --> 00:40:05,660
Your Highness,

624
00:40:07,140 --> 00:40:09,580
before you left,

625
00:40:10,260 --> 00:40:12,340
His Majesty clearly wanted you to stay.

626
00:40:14,380 --> 00:40:17,140
If he did, he could say so.

627
00:40:17,820 --> 00:40:18,940
Like I could disobey his order.

628
00:40:20,660 --> 00:40:23,500
His Majesty is a gentleman.

629
00:40:24,060 --> 00:40:25,540
He wouldn’t force you

630
00:40:26,380 --> 00:40:27,980
to do anything against your will.

631
00:40:30,660 --> 00:40:31,860
How did you know?

632
00:40:32,940 --> 00:40:34,060
Liaozi said so.

633
00:40:37,460 --> 00:40:38,300
Besides,

634
00:40:39,460 --> 00:40:41,180
you know he’s a nice man.

635
00:40:45,300 --> 00:40:46,420
Of course he is,

636
00:40:48,620 --> 00:40:52,020
but he married Guo before me.

637
00:40:52,820 --> 00:40:53,740
Although she was deposed,

638
00:40:54,860 --> 00:40:56,420
he still cares about her.

639
00:40:58,380 --> 00:40:59,540
There’s Madam Miao

640
00:41:00,220 --> 00:41:01,780
whom he is closest to

641
00:41:02,540 --> 00:41:04,020
and adores the most.

642
00:41:06,700 --> 00:41:08,180
And he loves Miss Chen so much

643
00:41:08,740 --> 00:41:10,420
that he doesn’t want to cage her in the palace.

644
00:41:12,740 --> 00:41:14,580
His Majesty opened his heart to you.

645
00:41:15,620 --> 00:41:16,300
That...

646
00:41:17,780 --> 00:41:19,060
That means he trusts you.

647
00:41:21,780 --> 00:41:23,100
He does trust me.

648
00:41:25,540 --> 00:41:26,540
He knows

649
00:41:28,060 --> 00:41:29,580
I can be a good empress.

650
00:41:40,300 --> 00:41:41,220
Anyway,

651
00:41:43,860 --> 00:41:45,260
I’m already his wife

652
00:41:46,940 --> 00:41:48,620
and no longer a Cao.

653
00:41:49,420 --> 00:41:50,500
I can’t be willful,

654
00:41:51,260 --> 00:41:53,260
or I’d be no different from Guo.

655
00:41:56,100 --> 00:41:57,420
He’s invested his trust in me,

656
00:41:58,660 --> 00:42:00,220
so I cannot

657
00:42:00,460 --> 00:42:01,900
disappoint him.

658
00:42:03,860 --> 00:42:05,660
I couldn’t stay with him

659
00:42:07,540 --> 00:42:08,620
because I was afraid

660
00:42:08,620 --> 00:42:10,460
I’d lose control

661
00:42:11,060 --> 00:42:12,020
and let my unhappiness out.

662
00:42:15,100 --> 00:42:18,220
Well, everything will be fine.

663
00:42:20,860 --> 00:42:22,140
I keep telling myself,

664
00:42:23,700 --> 00:42:24,820
“Don’t hold any grudge”.

665
00:42:25,780 --> 00:42:26,860
“You can’t hold any grudge”.

666
00:42:29,180 --> 00:42:30,060
Gradually,

667
00:42:32,180 --> 00:42:33,260
there is no grudge left.

668
00:42:36,220 --> 00:42:37,020
Your Highness…

669
00:42:42,180 --> 00:42:43,180
His Majesty

670
00:42:43,700 --> 00:42:45,860
will head to the southern suburb in a few days.

671
00:42:46,100 --> 00:42:47,620
Preparations need to be made in advance.

672
00:42:49,860 --> 00:42:51,460
I can’t be distracted

673
00:42:51,580 --> 00:42:52,660
or drown myself in sorrow.

674
00:42:53,860 --> 00:42:56,900
Huan, burn the sleeping incense.

675
00:42:58,780 --> 00:42:59,940
I need an early night.

676
00:43:04,420 --> 00:43:05,140
Yes.

677
00:43:36,260 --> 00:43:39,340
♪ Isolated kite ♪

678
00:43:39,340 --> 00:43:42,420
♪ Left everything behind ♪

679
00:43:42,420 --> 00:43:45,740
♪ Lost soul ♪

680
00:43:45,740 --> 00:43:48,900
♪ Can’t feel cause he can’t love ♪

681
00:43:48,900 --> 00:43:52,020
♪ Fondness is a beam of light ♪

682
00:43:52,020 --> 00:43:55,140
♪ Shines in the dark ♪

683
00:43:55,140 --> 00:43:58,220
♪ That overshines stars ♪

684
00:43:58,220 --> 00:44:05,060
♪ And nourishes all living things ♪

685
00:44:05,820 --> 00:44:08,540
♪ Those who love more are always hurt
by who love less ♪

686
00:44:08,540 --> 00:44:12,540
♪ I don’t want to remember, but I can’t forget ♪

687
00:44:12,540 --> 00:44:18,580
♪ My hair turns grey too soon
Laughing at me for being so sentimental ♪

688
00:44:18,580 --> 00:44:21,220
♪ Those who love more are always hurt
by who love less ♪

689
00:44:21,220 --> 00:44:25,180
♪ I love you so much, and hope you are well ♪

690
00:44:25,180 --> 00:44:31,540
♪ Towards the direction of light ♪

691
00:44:31,540 --> 00:44:37,780
♪ Light it up for the people ♪

692
00:44:37,780 --> 00:44:43,940
♪ Cure the heartless injury ♪

693
00:44:56,220 --> 00:44:59,860
♪ Those who love more are always hurt
by who love less ♪

694
00:44:59,860 --> 00:45:03,060
♪ I love you so much, and hope you are well ♪

695
00:45:03,060 --> 00:45:06,180
♪ When and where are we now ♪

696
00:45:06,180 --> 00:45:09,380
♪ I’m left alone, sobbing ♪

697
00:45:09,380 --> 00:45:12,420
♪ I love you so deeply that left
everything behind ♪

698
00:45:12,420 --> 00:45:14,820
♪ Life is always filled
with the sadness of parting ♪

699
00:45:14,820 --> 00:45:18,780
♪ Forget the past and revenge with a smile,
leave all the obsession behind ♪

700
00:45:18,780 --> 00:45:22,020
♪ We look at each other without words ♪

701
